{"type": "article", "id": 5114, "title": "B&O Play H8 无线头戴式耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-12T07:55:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052337597ktAglEmHyhFTCPd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t丹麦顶级视听品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 继 2014 年底发布 H2 头戴式耳机后，最近又带来了一款 B&amp;O Play H8 无线头戴式耳机。H8 放弃了传统的线缆设计，无线设计使得 H8 更具便携功能。除了无线设计之外，H8 还配置了主动降噪、触控等功能，用户可以通过触控来播放音乐、切换音乐和来电接听等基础功能，定价 499 美元（约合人民币 3667 元），预计 2 月在 Bang &amp; Olufsen 制定零售商和线上商铺正式发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233757UcDJgjs02SfYrnBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233757IWYxbFtpGjnaZ1rg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233758l8Wdw7pTO6rZmDjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233758k1oaJZg7bXeiINnu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233759WJBhNXE2gZoCaAnM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}